  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Test Your Focus and Coordination</h2><br>Urban Flow is all about making sure the cars drive safely in the city. That's where you come in - you control the traffic lights to make sure there are no accidents or traffic delays.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235340/extras/935ae4c7710c20a5e5429f4d18d72f40.poster.avif?t=1704295118\" width=640 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235340/extras/935ae4c7710c20a5e5429f4d18d72f40.webm?t=1704295118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235340/extras/935ae4c7710c20a5e5429f4d18d72f40.mp4?t=1704295118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Keep the City Safe</h2><br>Keep the cars moving in perfect harmony, and avoid crashes and jams to ensure everything runs smoothly. It's up to you to control the city's streets and make sure everyone gets to their destination on time. Over 100 levels, each with its own busy intersection.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235340/extras/43a10c319942b8827bf5602511f22e2b.poster.avif?t=1704295118\" width=640 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235340/extras/43a10c319942b8827bf5602511f22e2b.webm?t=1704295118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235340/extras/43a10c319942b8827bf5602511f22e2b.mp4?t=1704295118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Ensure a Smooth Ride</h2><br>Explore a vibrant city filled with cars, buses, and trucks, and take on increasingly challenging levels. Use your wits to navigate complex intersections and avoid accidents, all while managing multiple lanes of traffic at once.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235340/extras/7e0cee548c78a589073bac1e7f8525f2.poster.avif?t=1704295118\" width=640 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235340/extras/7e0cee548c78a589073bac1e7f8525f2.webm?t=1704295118\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235340/extras/7e0cee548c78a589073bac1e7f8525f2.mp4?t=1704295118\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gather Your Friends and Family</h2><br>Enjoy the game with up to four players in local co-op mode. With easy-to-learn gameplay and intuitive controls, Urban Flow is the perfect game to enjoy with friends and family, both young and old. So gather around and experience the fun and excitement of managing the flow of traffic together! <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2235340/extras/c800c43888ff678b7fd2be82e53944f8.avif?t=1704295118\" width=620 height=194 /></span>",
